title.rendered: Kendall and Kylie Jenner: The OK! Photo Shoot

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Kendall and Kylie Jenner have officially arrived… as supermarket tabloid fodder.

The half-sisters of three women who rake in millions a year by simply posing for magazines, these girls learned from the best. Or worst, depending on your perspective.

Featured in he latest edition of OK! Weekly, Kylie says: “I’m looking forward to high school and I still haven’t really figured out what I want to do yet.” But if she aims to be like Kourtney, Khloe or Kim Kardashian, the answer can be: nothing. These people are just professionally famous.

Kendall, meanwhile, has already sparked controversy by posing in a skimpy bikini. But she and her sister at least keep it entirely clean in the images below. Click on each to enlarge…
